45c833a2f1dd7cd1ea2fd3d8d41abb49c97d860ddec000ba6b39d90fa296d38b  fix-fetch-to-nfs.patch"
sha512sums="962710cba13f713f4fc7b6ac5851cbe4d7a6e6a13b629ca73af1eb521e84f80160a98df6c611d89c92db41c0192762db41783158774820827776a1251ca33bf2  abuild-2.20.1.tar.xz
1276500dd4ffbb26adb2f25443575a0ea5ba3ffe71189587d880f424818dd6ac4bd95fbfb181d3214245a87c9f4c26b9d3ceb015d224f5c162581e027b55b494  fix-fetch-to-nfs.patch"
